room_title: Escape room "FBI Mafia Investigation" by Urban Escape Games in Atlanta
room_address: 20 Mansell Court East, Suite #275, Alpharetta, GA 30076
room_description: Your team has been assigned to investigate the Vinny's Pizzeria. A source says that's where the Mafia has their secret lair. To prove yourselves as real FBI agents, you have to sneak in and gather the evidence. Be careful, you only have an hour!
